OL,3,CConcerns over cancer care after
OL,4,Ccharity refuses to rule out closure
OL,6,FNurses say the 26-bed unit at the
OL,7,Fhospice in Woolton, Liverpool, was
OL,8,Fclosed in summer 2024, and today the
OL,9,Farea's MP said she has been told one
OL,10,Fof the options may be to close the
OL,11,Funit permanently.
OL,13,FIt has also added to the anxiety of
OL,14,Fthose who are not only dealing with
OL,15,Fthe uncertainty of the condition, but
OL,16,Fnow also the possibility of losing
OL,17,Fwhat's been described as "a vital
OL,18,Fservice".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
