OL,3,CConcerns over cancer care after
OL,4,Ccharity refuses to rule out closure
OL,6,FClare Beloved's wife Sandra Richardson
OL,7,Freceived care at the unit and is just
OL,8,Fone of thousands of people it has
OL,9,Fhelped.
OL,11,FWhen she was struck down by secondary
OL,12,Fbreast cancer she decided she wanted
OL,13,Fto die at home in Toxteth but changed
OL,14,Fher mind when the pain became too much
OL,15,Fto bear and she moved onto the
OL,16,Fpalliative care unit.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
