OL,3,CConcerns over cancer care after
OL,4,Ccharity refuses to rule out closure
OL,6,FClare says: "The night before Sandra
OL,7,Fdied we were able to wheel her outside
OL,8,Fand amid the flowers at the beautiful
OL,9,Fgarden at Marie Curie, and she watched
OL,10,Fthe sunset, and that would never have
OL,11,Fhappened in a hospital corridor or a
OL,12,Fhome.
OL,14,F"Beautiful memories to carry us
OL,15,Fforward."
OL,17,FBut one former nurse says that there
OL,18,Fare no longer staff there to care for
OL,19,Fpatients on the inpatient unit and
OL,20,Fthat it has been closed since last
OL,21,FJuly.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
