OL,3,CConcerns over cancer care after
OL,4,Ccharity refuses to rule out closure
OL,6,FLucy Williams is now an independent
OL,7,Fcouncillor and says that her former
OL,8,Fcolleagues have come to her saying the
OL,9,Funit's been shut and that they were
OL,10,Ftold the closure is due to staff
OL,11,Fshortages.
OL,13,FShe has organised a peaceful protest
OL,14,Fand is demanding answers from the
OL,15,Fcharity.
OL,17,FShe says: "On Saturday for the public
OL,18,Fto come along and show that they stand
OL,19,Fwith the staff here for Marie Curie
OL,20,Fwould mean a lot.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
