OL,3,CConcerns over cancer care after
OL,4,Ccharity refuses to rule out closure
OL,6,F"The staff here are upset, they're
OL,7,Ffearful for their jobs and they're
OL,8,Ffearful for the community as well and
OL,9,Ffuture patients."
OL,11,FIn statement local Maria Eagle MP said
OL,12,Fthe charity was "considering all
OL,13,Foptions".
OL,15,FShe said: "I met with Marie Curie
OL,16,Fnational management. They assured me
OL,17,Fthat they are fundamentally committed
OL,18,Fto providing palliative care services
OL,19,Fin Liverpool now and in the future.
OL,21,F"They do so every day.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
